Package grafioschtrader.entities

Class HoldCashaccountBalance

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.entities.HoldBase
grafioschtrader.entities.HoldCashaccountBalance
@Entity public class HoldCashaccountBalance extends HoldBase
It is a snapshot for the cash account. When a relevant transaction takes place on it, a period is opened and the previously opened period is closed with it.

Each record corresponds to a period in which one or more cash-account transactions occurred, categorizing the net effect of deposits/withdrawals, interest, fees, security buys/sells, and dividends. The balance reflects the end-of-period cash balance, with currency conversion factors applied via embedded currency pair references for tenant and portfolio.

This entity maps to the hold_cashaccount_balance table and is not exposed via the public REST API.
